content:
Customize Your UI with Lightning Web Components

To update the look and feel of your customer-facing messaging interface, create and add Lightning Web Components.

Available in: Lightning Experience. View required editions 
This article applies to: Messaging for In-App and Messaging for Web channels
Create a Lightning web component.
From Setup, Enter Embedded Service Deployments, and select Embedded Service Deployments.
Click the downward arrow to the right of your deployment, and select View.
Click Add Custom UI Components.
Select a component from the Custom Component dropdown that corresponds with the desired standard UI element.
Save your changes.
Publish your deployment.
title: Customizing Service Cloud UI with Lightning Web Components
